        "category": "summary",
        "text": "Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to cause a permanent denial-of-service condition by sending specially crafted TCP packets. This condition would then require a device reboot.",
        "title": "Risk evaluation"
      },
      {
        "category": "other",
